<div style="margin-left: 1px;" class="row justify-content-between">

    <h2 class="col-6">刊登新職缺</h2>
    <span class="remark col-6 text-end"><em>＊</em>為必填項目</span>
</div>

<ol class="stepsBox">
    <li class="is-doing col-12 col-lg-3">1.填寫工作內容與職缺資訊</li>
    <li class=" col-12 col-lg-3">2.填寫職缺條件</li>
    <li class=" col-12 col-lg-3">3.填寫應徵與面試</li>
    <li class=" col-12 col-lg-3">4.觀看預覽</li>
</ol>

<div class="col-lg-12">
    <div class="job-content">

        <div class="card card-no-radius mb-3">
            <div class="card-header card-title-p">
                <div class="fw-bold d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                    <span>工作內容與職缺資訊</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body text-secondary">

                <table class="table table-striped table-rwd ">

