                                </div>
                                <p class="mark-text-red">
                                    依就業服務法規定，雇主不得於予就業歧視，例:女服務人員、倉管人員(限男性)。
                                    <span><a href="#" class="mark-text-blue">就業服務法</a></span>
                                </p>
                            </td>
                        </tr>


                        <tr>
                            <td><span class="text-danger p-1">*</span>工作內容：</td>
                            <td>
                                <div class="mb-3">
                                    <label for="JobDescription" class="form-label"><a href="#">[使用範本]</a></label>
                                    <textarea class="form-control" id="JobDescription" rows="3"></textarea>
                                </div>
                            </td>
                        </tr>


                        <tr class="opening-category">
                            <td><span class="mark-text-red p-1">*</span>薪資待遇：</td>
                            <td id="SalaryPayment">
                                <div class="form-check text-start">
                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="SalaryPayment" id="SalaryPayment1">
                                    <label class="form-check-label" for="SalaryPayment1">
